mgbagwoju geometry: Ọmụmụ ihe owuwu geometric na ihe owuwu na-esite na, ma ọ bụ kọwapụtara ya, ọnụọgụ mgbagwoju anya
\u1ecdn\u1ee5\u1ecdg\u1ee5g\u1ee5 mgbagw: Ọnụọgụ nke ụdị a + bi ebe a na b bụ ọnụọgụgụ n'ezie
ezigbo ak\u1ee5k\u1ee5: Okwu dị na nọmba mgbagwoju anya nke na-enweghị nkeji echiche dị ka ihe kpatara ya
ak\u1ee5k\u1ee5 echiche: Akụkụ nke nọmba mgbagwoju anya nke nwere nkeji echiche dị ka ihe kpatara ya
mgbagwoju manifolds: Oghere dị na geometry gbagwojuru anya bụ mkpokọta akụkụ nke akụkụ na elu
mgbagwoju algebra iche: Oghere dị na geometry gbagwojuru anya bụ ihe ngwọta maka nhatanha polynomial
ihe owuwu holomorphic: Ihe owuwu na geometry mgbagwoju anya nke dị mgbagwoju anya-iche
mmemme ihe nlereanya pere mpe: Mmemme na geometry dị mgbagwoju anya maka nhazi nke manifolds dị mgbagwoju anya na ụdị algebra dị mgbagwoju anya
oghere moduli: Oghere dị na geometry gbagwojuru anya nke na-ekpebi ụfọdụ ụdị ihe geometric
calabi conjections: Echiche dị na geometry gbagwojuru anya nke Shing-Tung Yau gosipụtara gbasara ịdị adị nke ụdị metric pụrụ iche n'ọtụtụ dị mgbagwoju anya.
hitchin-kobayashi akw\u1ee5kw\u1ecd ozi: Mpempe akwụkwọ ozi na geometry gbagwojuru anya n'etiti ngwugwu holomorphic vector kwụsiri ike na azịza maka otu nhata dị iche.
akw\u1ee5kw\u1ecd ozi nonabelian hodge: Akwụkwọ ozi dị na geometry gbagwojuru anya n'etiti ụfọdụ ụdị manifold dị mgbagwoju anya na ụfọdụ ụdị ihe owuwu algebra
kahler-einstein metrics: Ụdị metrik pụrụ iche n'ụdị dị mgbagwoju anya nke na-eju ọnọdụ ụfọdụ
